articles.author: Mitchell McCluskey, Sophie Tanno
articles.title: Romania’s pro-EU candidate beats hard-right rival to win presidential election - CNN
articles.description: Romania’s pro-European Union presidential candidate Nicușor Dan won the country’s presidential election Sunday, defeating his ultranationalist rival.
articles.content:
